Arinze Obiora (amuru 5 Disemba 1985) bu onye amala elu Naijiria lara ezumike nka
Ọ gụchara nke anọ na asọmpi Africa niile n'afọ 2003, isii na asọmpị Afrịka 2006, nwetere nrite ọla n'asọmpị Africa niile nke 2007 wee gụchaa nke isii na asọmpi Afrịka 2008
Ihe kacha mma ya bụ mita 2.20, nwetara na July 2007 na Algiers
